Are you... okay?

00:04:01.652 --> 00:04:02.878
Miss...

00:04:08.566 --> 00:04:11.166
if I had another chance,

00:04:21.700 --> 00:04:23.366
it'd be my turn to walk towards you.

00:04:25.829 --> 00:04:27.367
♪ Every day and every night ♪

